brew install htop-osx

brew install git hub tmux

brew install vim

brew cask install android-file-transfer appcleaner iterm2 pomello slack spotify spotify-notifications selfcontrol skype teamviewer utorrent vlc

brew cask install firefox firefoxdeveloperedition google-chrome google-chrome-canary opera

brew cask install diffmerge

brew cleanup
